# REST Client test file (VS Code REST Client extension)
# Run each request by clicking "Send Request" above it

@base = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{base}}/api/health

### Full resume
GET {{base}}/api/resume

### Bio only
GET {{base}}/api/resume/bio

### Experience
GET {{base}}/api/resume/experience

### Education
GET {{base}}/api/resume/education

### Skills
GET {{base}}/api/resume/skills
